w quests, festivals, and even villager outfits! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/ac53494cf019ab6d3003162681b9a3c9.webp?t=1771865130\" width=22 height=16 /></span> Get to know 30+ villagers and follow their stories </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/be8f692ae78e347c7346f889c0cf32dc.webp?t=1771865130\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Battle foes and discover treasures as you explore ancient ruins  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/e1f358796e64a098700a2513f69f9c8f.webp?t=1771865130\" width=16 height=16 /></span> And so much more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/c452523f30af1e92a24440a988065ae5.apng?t=1771865130\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/c452523f30af1e92a24440a988065ae5.poster.avif?t=1771865130\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=81 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/288eb428ac558857c038a54c81c0be3e.avif?t=1771865130\" width=600 height=742 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/fec959711842d25d848148e030f8102b.apng?t=1771865130\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142790/extras/fec959711842d25d848148e030f8102b.poster.avif?t